  "name": "Sadist's Lash",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p>This barbed whip writhes with cruel enchantment magic. The Sadist's Lash is a +2 striking wounding whip with 15 feet reach.</p><hr /><p><strong>Activate</strong> <span class=\"action-glyph\">A</span> (manipulate)</p><p><strong>Requirements</strong> You are holding the Sadist's Lash and have an enchantment spell with a range of touch prepared or in your repertoire.</p><p><strong>Effect</strong> Increase the casting time of the enchantment spell by one action. Make a Strike with the lash as part of the activity, delivering the spell on a successful hit. On a critical success, the target is also @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.TBSHQspnbcqxsmjL]{Stupefied 1} until the start of your next turn.</p>"
    },
